  "response_text": "A close view begins on the back pocket of an adult wearing light gray pants and a blue denim shirt. A folded Luvs diaper sticks out of the pocket like a handy tool, its white and purple waistband visible and the purple “Luvs” logo facing outward. The adult’s rolled sleeve and wristwatch are visible beside the pocket, with greenery and a park path blurred in the background.\n\nThe scene opens wider in a tree-lined park. A father-presenting adult with curly hair walks toward the viewer along a broad path. He wears a blue shirt with a dark vest or carrier straps, light pants, and sneakers. A smiling baby rides against his chest in a black front carrier, wearing a pale yellow top. In one hand, he pulls or guides a small purple children’s tricycle with turquoise wheels. Other people move in the background, including someone with a bicycle, reinforcing the busy public-park setting.\n\nNear the ground, a toddler girl in a white long-sleeved top, pale blue skirt, white socks, and pink shoes crouches at the edge of a shallow puddle in the path. The adult’s legs and the purple tricycle are nearby. Holding the adult’s hand above her, she springs up and across the wet spot; her skirt flares and her ponytail swings as her feet lift off the ground. She lands with the adult still supporting her by the hand, smiling and animated, while the father continues managing both children and the tricycle.\n\nThe father with the baby pauses and looks ahead with a calm, knowing expression. The baby in the carrier smiles broadly beneath him, framed by tall green trees and soft daylight.\n\nA different parent sits on a wooden park bench, changing a baby on a gray changing pad. A large gray diaper bag rests to the baby’s side. This second adult, wearing a plaid shirt and jeans, bends over the baby and holds the baby’s legs up while dealing with a white diaper. The baby lies on its back in a blue-and-white striped shirt and appears upset, with a crying expression. As the diaper is shown, bold white block text appears at the lower left: “CHEAP LEAKY DIAPERS.”\n\nThe first father, still carrying the baby on his chest, looks toward the bench and then brings a Luvs diaper into view. He offers the folded diaper outward, its purple waistband and “Luvs” logo visible. The other parent’s face appears at the right edge, looking toward the offered diaper. A purple graphic shape appears behind the diaper with white text reading “pro level” and smaller text beneath it reading “LEAK PROTECTION.” Hands from both adults meet around the diaper as it is passed along, visually presenting Luvs as the replacement for the leaky diaper.\n\nThe commercial ends on a simple product display: a purple box of Luvs diapers sits centered against a pale lavender background. The front of the box shows the large white-and-green “Luvs” logo and a photo of a baby, with the packaging cleanly lit and isolated as the final image.",
